{
  "stem": "14091.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was when the two synagogues was burned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then they started to catch children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They wanted only children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My mother used to hide me under piles of things and-- because I was the smallest at that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they still managed and they weed out many.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This-- to be in the ghetto was very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The winter were fierce.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The hunger, it was impossible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The things that we had was finished in a very short time, and they-- we didn't get any rations.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Only they gave us the flour that my mother used to bake.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And some people used to come out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean, they would sneak out of the ghetto and go, and they would bring some kind of food, some kind of things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And people used to get caught.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And of course, when you were caught, you were shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this went on like that, until spring came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they were taking the healthier people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they put them to dig for-- although it was winter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they put them to dig.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, we didn't know why they were digging.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this was quite a way from the city, and they dug big pits.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Some other people, younger people, women and other, work for the gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to work in the kitchens, they used to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But at that time, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my-- I was with my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But my sisters did work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And also they worked, they had like seamstresses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were sewing, I don't know for whom, but they were working as seamstresses.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And cobblers were working, doing boots.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
